Expand description

The error type for I/O operations of the [`Read`](trait.Read.html "trait std::io::Read"), [`Write`](trait.Write.html "trait std::io::Write"), [`Seek`](trait.Seek.html "trait std::io::Seek"), and associated traits.

Errors mostly originate from the underlying OS, but custom instances of `Error` can be created with crafted error messages and a particular value of [`ErrorKind`](enum.ErrorKind.html "enum std::io::ErrorKind").

